<p class="en">This diagnosis builds on the earlier pieces covering the <a href="/en/blog/etf-issuer-flip-short-liquidation-gap">ETF issuer money rotation</a>, the <a href="/en/blog/options-skew-not-confirming-rebound">options skew check</a>, the <a href="/en/blog/fear-greed-whiplash-btc-range-intact">Fear & Greed whiplash diagnosis</a>, and the <a href="/en/blog/etf-first-negative-half-leverage-buildup-gap">three-way split among exchange reserves, ETFs, and leverage</a>.</p>
